annotation: More biographical information that builds in part on the preceding memorate. Margrete's response is far more concise than Tang Kristensen likely expected. This short response was never published.
danish_manuscript:
A var Pige til 30 Aar, gift i 26, nu enke
i 25. Det er mit Levnetsbeskrivelse.
english_manuscript: I was a hired girl until I was thirty, married for twenty-six years, and now a widow for twenty-five years. That's my life story.
english_publication: Unpublished version reads: I was a hired girl until I was thirty, married for twenty-six years, and now a widow for twenty-five years. That’s my life story.
